function asignar_funcion(){

if(!Modernizr.canvas) {
$('#sb_searchtext').each(function() {
if ($(this).val() == (($('#sb_cat').val() == '0')?'ej: piso, BMW, iphone4...':miArray[$('#sb_cat').val()])) {
$(this).val('');
}
//<![CDATA[
if ($(this).val() == '' && !$(this).is(':focus')) {
$('#sb_searchtext').css('color','#999');
if($('#sb_cat').val() == '0')
$(this).val('ej: piso, BMW, iphone4..');
else
$(this).val(miArray[$('#sb_cat').val()]);
}
//]]>
$(this).focus(function(){
$('#sb_searchtext').css('color','#000');
if ($(this).val().substr(0,3) =="ej:") {
$(this).val('');
}else{
$(this).val($('#sb_searchtext').val());
};
});
$(this).blur(function(){
if( $(this).val() == '' ) {
if($('#sb_cat').val() == '0')
$(this).val('ej: piso, BMW, iphone4...');
else
$(this).val(miArray[$('#sb_cat').val()]);
if($(this).val().substr(0,3) =="ej:" )
$('#sb_searchtext').css('color','#999');
else
$('#sb_searchtext').css('color','#000');
}else{
$(this).val($('#sb_searchtext').val());
$('#sb_searchtext').css('color','#000');
searchtextChanged=1;
};
});
});

function updateParentIframeSize( _localObjectId, _parentIframeId,_nodomchange ){
_nodomchange = (typeof(_nodomchange) == 'undefined') ? 0 : _nodomchange;

var height = 0;
//<![CDATA[
if ((window.location.hostname == "dev.segundamano.es") && (_nodomchange==0 ) ) {
document.domain="dev.segundamano.es";
} else {
}
//]]>

if (document.body.scrollHeight > document.body.offsetHeight) { // all but Explorer Mac
var obj = document.getElementById(_localObjectId);
if ( obj )
height = obj.scrollHeight;
if (height == 15)
height = 0;
} else { // works in Explorer 6 Strict, Mozilla (not FF) and Safari
var obj = document.getElementById(_localObjectId);
if ( obj )
height = obj.offsetHeight;
}

try{
parent.document.getElementById( _parentIframeId ).height=height;
var iframe_header = parent.document.getElementById( _parentIframeId + "_anuncios_similares_no_q");
//<![CDATA[
if ( height > 0 && iframe_header ) {
iframe_header.style.display = "block";
parent.document.getElementById( _parentIframeId).style.display = "block";
}else{
if (height == 0){
parent.document.getElementById(_parentIframeId).style.display = "none";
}
}
//]]>
} catch (e) {
}
}

function setTop(ob,n){
/* Solo numeros */
if (/[^0-9]/.test(ob.value[ob.value.length-1])) ob.value=ob.value.slice(0,ob.value.length-1)
if (ob.value.length>n) {
ob.value=ob.value.slice(0,ob.value.length-1)
}
}

$('#clearFilters').click(function() {

document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function(event) {
showActiveFiltersNumber();
});

function updateFiltersNumberOnlyWhenFiltersMenuNotActive() {
if ($('#filtersBoxMsite').hasClass('active') === false) {
showActiveFiltersNumber();
}
}

function showActiveFiltersNumber() {
if (activeFiltersNum>0){
document.getElementById( 'filtesActive' ).innerHTML = "<i class='greenText'>(&nbsp;</i>" + activeFiltersNum + "<i class='greenText'>&nbsp;)</i>";
document.getElementById( 'filtesActive' ).style.display = 'inline-block';
document.getElementById( 'filtesActive2' ).innerHTML = "<i class='greenText'>(&nbsp;</i>" + activeFiltersNum + "<i class='greenText'>&nbsp;)</i>";
document.getElementById( 'filtesActive2' ).style.display = 'inline-block';
}else {
document.getElementById( 'filtesActive' ).style.display = 'none';
document.getElementById( 'filtesActive2' ).style.display = 'none';
}

var priceFilterLink = document.getElementById( 'priceFilterLink' );
var filterBy1 = document.getElementById( 'filterBy1' );
var filterBy2 = document.getElementById( 'filterBy2' );
var viewFilters = {
filterByPrice: function() {
classie.toggle( priceFilterLink, 'show' );
}
};

if ( filterBy1 != null ){
filterBy1.onclick = function(e) {
e.preventDefault();
viewFilters.filterByPrice();
return false;
};
}

if ( filterBy2 != null ){
filterBy2.onclick = function(e) {
e.preventDefault();
viewFilters.filterByPrice();
return false;
};
}
}

</script>
